Definition:
	Comments make code easier to read, and help guide other programmers through your thought processes.

Syntax
	// comment

	/*  this is
	*  a mult-line
	*  comment
	*/

Examples:

class Comment {
public:
	method 1; // this is a comment example.
	...
private:
	/* this is a
	* multiline
	* comment example
	*/

	variable 1;
	...
}
